data.description: Amazing views of the harbor & Cascade Mountain Range. Perfectly situated moments from waterfront trails at Windjammer Park, & close to shopping, restaurants, schools & NAS Whidbey. The primary bedroom features two spacious closets, windows with tranquil garden views & 3/4 bath including double vanity & private water closet. Two guest bedrooms, one featuring custom built-ins, french doors & murphy bed for flexibility. Spacious living & dining area with cozy fireplace leading to your covered balcony. Kitchen features upgraded granite countertops & plenty of storage including walk-in pantry. The Heat Pump with Central A/C will keep you comfortable even in the peak of Summer. Enjoy the elevator & designated covered parking, & storage closet!
